  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/32px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br><i>Only during the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Category:Events\" title=\"Category:Events\">Event</a>:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Winter%27s_Feast\" title=\"Winter&#x27;s Feast\"><img alt=\"Festive Tree Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Festive_Tree_Icon.png/50px-Festive_Tree_Icon.png?8bcacc\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\"></a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Winter%27s_Feast\" title=\"Winter&#x27;s Feast\">Winter&#x27;s Feast</a><br>\n</p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<div><b>“</b><span>Standing near this device will provide the survivor with special crafting options of &quot;Winters Feast food&quot; they can start cooking at this oven.</span><b>”</b>\n<p>-<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Scrapbook\" title=\"Scrapbook Description\"><img alt=\"Scrapbook Description\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Lost_Scrapbook_Page.png/50px-Lost_Scrapbook_Page.png?f37463\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\"></a></p>\n</div>\n<p>The <b>Masonry Oven</b> is a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Structures\" title=\"Structures\">Structure</a> introduced in 2019. It requires 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cut_Stone\" title=\"Cut Stone\">Cut Stone</a>, 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Marble\" title=\"Marble\">Marble</a> and 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Log\" title=\"Log\">Log</a> to craft. When standing close to a Masonry Oven, players are able to access the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Winter%27s_Feast_Cooking_Filter\" title=\"Winter&#x27;s Feast Cooking Filter\">Winter&#x27;s Feast Cooking Filter</a>.\n</p>\n<div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Crafting_Recipes\">Crafting Recipes</span></h2>\n<div><ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Merry_Berrysauce\" title=\"Merry Berrysauce\"><img alt=\"Merry Berrysauce\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Merry_Berrysauce.png?c5b358\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Merry_Berrysauce\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Merry Berrysauce\">Merry Berrysauce</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Bibingka\" title=\"Bibingka\"><img alt=\"Bibingka\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Bibingka.png?c22cfa\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Bibingka\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bibingka\">Bibingka</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cabbage_Rolls\" title=\"Cabbage Rolls\"><img alt=\"Cabbage Rolls\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Cabbage_Rolls.png?2b48f5\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cabbage_Rolls\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Cabbage Rolls\">Cabbage Rolls</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Festive_Fish_Dish\" title=\"Festive Fish Dish\"><img alt=\"Festive Fish Dish\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Festive_Fish_Dish.png?11f941\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Festive_Fish_Dish\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Festive Fish Dish\">Festive Fish Dish</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Good_Gravy\" title=\"Good Gravy\"><img alt=\"Good Gravy\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Good_Gravy.png?5943c9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Good_Gravy\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Good Gravy\">Good Gravy</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Latkes\" title=\"Latkes\"><img alt=\"Latkes\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Latkes.png?5e9832\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Latkes\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Latkes\">Latkes</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lutefisk\" title=\"Lutefisk\"><img alt=\"Lutefisk\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Lutefisk.png?4d1acd\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lutefisk\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lutefisk\">Lutefisk</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Mulled_Punch\" title=\"Mulled Punch\"><img alt=\"Mulled Punch\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Mulled_Punch.png?85047e\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Mulled_Punch\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Mulled Punch\">Mulled Punch</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Panett