lass=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pumpkin_Pie\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Pumpkin Pie\">Pumpkin Pie</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Roasted_Turkey\" title=\"Roasted Turkey\"><img alt=\"Roasted Turkey\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Roasted_Turkey.png?802d77\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Roasted_Turkey\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Roasted Turkey\">Roasted Turkey</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Stuffing\" title=\"Stuffing\"><img alt=\"Stuffing\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Stuffing.png?282823\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Stuffing\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Stuffing\">Stuffing</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sweet_Potato_Casserole\" title=\"Sweet Potato Casserole\"><img alt=\"Sweet Potato Casserole\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Sweet_Potato_Casserole.png?e00037\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sweet_Potato_Casserole\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sweet Potato Casserole\">Sweet Potato Casserole</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Tamales\" title=\"Tamales\"><img alt=\"Tamales\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Tamales.png?45a43b\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Tamales\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Tamales\">Tamales</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Tourtiere\" title=\"Tourtiere\"><img alt=\"Tourtiere\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Tourtiere.png?54cb02\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Tourtiere\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Tourtiere\">Tourtiere</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gallery\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blueprint\" title=\"Blueprint\"><img alt=\"Blueprint.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Blueprint.png/32px-Blueprint.png?80b6b5\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Gallery</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Masonry_Oven_Build_Open.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Opened\"><img alt=\"Opened\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Masonry_Oven_Build_Open.png/114px-Masonry_Oven_Build_Open.png?a04931\" width=\"114\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Opened</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Masonry_Oven_Build_Cook.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Cooking\"><img alt=\"Cooking\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Masonry_Oven_Build_Cook.png/114px-Masonry_Oven_Build_Cook.png?f6e59b\" width=\"114\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Cooking</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Masonry_Oven_Burnt.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Unused Burnt Masonry Oven.\"><img alt=\"Unused Burnt Masonry Oven.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Masonry_Oven_Burnt.png/118px-Masonry_Oven_Burnt.png?c9b9b0\" width=\"118\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Unused Burnt Masonry Oven.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
